{"tid":1815780,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「集體炒車」 芬蘭政府澄清 無意推出四天工作週","createTime":"2020-01-07T18:50:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-07T18:50:40.000Z","uid":276715,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"fa617058a0d9fc621a183b8a1efac7e1a9cc6c75","tid":1815780,"uid":276715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T18:50:40.000Z","msg":"芬蘭政府澄清，上月上台的總理馬琳無意推出4天工作週。<br />\n<br />\n馬琳去年8月仍是運輸部長時，曾提出4天工作週的意念，近日不知何故，歐洲多間傳媒稱馬琳政府「已決定」推出4天工作週，但事實是目前的5黨聯合政府去年初夏才上台，原總理因為政治醜聞上月匆匆下台，馬琳臨危受命接任，但為了盡快平息醜聞引起的政治震盪，5黨同意維持原本的政治綱領，不作改動，內閣也只是換了兩、三個人便算。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://yle.fi/uutiset/osasto/news/govt_corrects_inaccurate_reports_on_finnish_pms_alleged_4-day_work_week/11146856\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyle.fi%2Fuutiset%2Fosasto%2Fnews%2Fgovt_corrects_inaccurate_reports_on_finnish_pms_alleged_4-day_work_week%2F11146856&d=rLp99s1CaA%2FTm5LA4NL6TbtFVp6nBI01qSlVibQweWg%3D&h=c1190481\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://yle.fi/uutiset/osasto/news/govt_corrects_inaccurate_reports_on_finnish_pms_alleged_4-day_work_week/11146856</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁都有得炒車 大家唔洗諗再移民芬蘭"}]}